name: G-01
introduce:
针对精细和难以顾及到的面部区域。它的尖端适合眼睑，
睫毛已经皮肤纹理的深处。而它的尾端可以很好的跟脸部轮廓想贴和，

适合：粉饼/腮红膏，尖端适合遮瑕膏！

For delicate and hard-to-reach facial areas. Its tip fits the eyelid,
The eyelashes are already deep in the skin texture. And the end of it fits in nicely with the outline of the face,
Not just any foundation sponge, that's for sure.
It is easy to control the amount of foundation, so that the foundation can be evenly applied to the surface, the effect is natural.
Fit: Powder/blush cream, tip for concealer!
